ca.usask.simlab.odeToJava.scheme

Class IMEXESDIRKButcherTableau

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.usask.simlab.odeToJava.scheme.Scheme
      • ca.usask.simlab.odeToJava.scheme.ARKButcherTableau
        • ca.usask.simlab.odeToJava.scheme.IMEXESDIRKButcherTableau

  • public class IMEXESDIRKButcherTableau
extends ARKButcherTableau
    Class that defines IMEX Butcher tableau with an explicit method as the first tableau and an explicit singly diagonally-implicit Runge-Kutta method as the second tableau, which has the first stage explicit in the tableau.

    Christopher A. Kennedy, Mark H. Carpenter. "Additive Runge-Kutta schemes for convection-diffusion-reaction equations.". Applied numerical mathematics, vol. 44, pg.139-181, 2003.

    Sebastiano Boscarino. "On an accurate third order implicit-explicit Runge-Kutta method for stiff problems", Applied Numerical Mathematics, vol. 59, pg. 1515-1528, 2009.
